  "description": "This image captures a serene coastal landscape bathed in the warm glow of either a sunrise or sunset. The foreground features a dark, silhouetted tree on the left edge, framing the expansive view.  The middle ground is a mix of urban development and natural landforms, including a coastline with a long pier or bridge extending into a calm bay. In the distance, a range of low hills or mountains forms the backdrop. The sky is dominated by dramatic, orange and grey clouds, seemingly lit from behind, creating a vibrant and textured display. The light reflects beautifully on the water, enhancing the sense of tranquility. A few birds are visible silhouetted against the bright sky.",
